(12, 1, '2011-02-15 02:22:48', '2011-02-15 02:22:48', 'Lindquist Realtors has been selling property in Prescott, Arizona since 1981. They already had a website, but they needed a new design to represent the realtors they are and the property they represent.\r\n\r\nThere logo and color theme was incorporated into a new design that gave their site a profesional look that showcased their realtors as well as their properties. They wanted the properties to be searchable by price, location, and facilities. They now have a search section in the sidebar of all theor pages for easy access to theor visitors.\r\n\r\nThey wanted to list properties available not just in Prescott, but in areas all over Northern Arizona. And not just their properties, but all the properties on the market. To do that a custom application had to be installed and manipulated to fit the design of the site.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.lindquistrealtors.com">www.lindquistrealtors.com</a>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">BEFORE</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Lindquist-Realtors_original.png"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-83" title="Lindquist Realtors_original" src="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Lindquist-Realtors_original-1024x792.png" alt="" width="362" height="279" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">AFTER</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Lindquist-Realtors1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-82" title="Lindquist Realtors" src="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Lindquist-Realtors1-632x1024.png" alt="" width="379" height="614" /></a></p>', 'Lindquist Realtors', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'lindquist-realtors', '', '', '2014-06-13 05:34:59', '2014-06-13 05:34:59', '', 0, 'http://third-law.com/?p=12', 0, 'post', '', 0),
