(85, 1, '2011-07-28 04:17:20', '2011-07-28 04:17:20', '[one_third]Lindquist Realtors has been selling property in Prescott, Arizona since 1981. They already had a website, but they needed a new design to represent the realtors they are and the property they represent.\r\n\r\nThere logo and color theme was incorporated into a new design that gave their site a profesional look that showcased their realtors as well as their properties. They wanted the properties to be searchable by price, loacation, and facilities. They now have a search section in the sidebar of all theor pages for easy access to theor visitors.\r\n\r\nThey wanted to list properties available not just in Prescott, but in areas all over Northern Arizona. And not just their properties, but all the properties on the market. To do that a custom application had to be installed and manipulated to fit the design of the site.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.lindquistrealtors.com">www.lindquistrealtors.com</a>[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[two_third_last]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Lindquist-Realtors_original.png"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-83" title="Lindquist Realtors_original" src="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Lindquist-Realtors_original-1024x792.png" alt="" width="362" height="279" /></a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Lindquist-Realtors1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-82" title="Lindquist Realtors" src="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Lindquist-Realtors1-632x1024.png" alt="" width="379" height="614" /></a>[/two_third_last]</p>', 'Lindquist Realtors', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2011-07-28 04:17:20', '2011-07-28 04:17:20', '', 12, 'http://third-law.com/12-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(15, 1, '2011-02-15 02:24:24', '2011-02-15 02:24:24', 'The Yavapai County Republican Committee needed a new look and that was provided by local Prescott ad agency, Helken and Horn. I took their excellent design and coded it into reality. The old site, besides not being too great to look at and hard to navigate was also hard to update. So we gave the design a Wordpress backend and made it super user friendly to add new articles and keep old pages up to date.\r\n\r\nFunctions that were hidden were brought front and center like the option to register to vote and to donate to the cause. Donations are accepted through the third party processing gateway so credit cards can be accepted. If they decide to sell items in the future, those functions are already built in. A fundraising thermometer was also added to create a visual of their progress and goals which takes less than a minute to update.\r\n\r\nA facelift of the site, a little tweak here and there, some added functionality, and the Yavapai Republicans have a great new site.\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">BEFORE</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/yavgop_orig1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-95" title="Yavapia County Republicans Old Site" src="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/yavgop_orig1-679x1024.png" alt="" width="326" height="491" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">AFTER</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Yavapai-County-Republican-Party1.png"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-74" title="Yavapai County Republican Party New Website" src="http://third-law.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Yavapai-County-Republican-Party1-763x1024.png" alt="" width="320" height="430" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Yavapai Republican Committee', 'The Yavapai Republican Committee needed a new look and that was provided by local Prescott ad agency, Helken and Horn. I took their excellent design and coded it into reality. The old site, besides not being too great to look at and hard to navigate was also hard to update. So we gave the design a Wordpress backend and made it super user friendly to add new articles and keep old pages up to date. ', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'yavapai-republican-committee', '', '', '2014-06-13 05:34:59', '2014-06-13 05:34:59', '', 0, 'http://third-law.com/?p=15', 0, 'post', '', 0),
